{"tid":2492482,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔上市｜譚仔姐姐人工原來有咁多！月薪竟高過全港一半打工仔？","createTime":"2021-04-17T06:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:30:40.000Z","uid":11148,"like":267,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"47becec7968c42a6b1917c02e03e2ddd340054a3","tid":2492482,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"譚仔米線深受港人歡迎，譚仔姐姐們亦常常引起港人熱論。不過不說不知道，原來譚仔姐姐每月人工隨時比你和我還要高！<br />\n<br />\n根據招聘網站Jooble，譚仔在最新4月8日的招聘日中，以每月薪金16,500至20,000元招聘「侍應／廚房助理／洗碗」，未<span class=\"red\">計及新人獎金、勤工獎、醫療和交通津貼，20000元月薪其實已比全港每月工資中位數多，即高過全港一半打工仔，更比製造、零售、物業管理、保安等行業還要高</span>。<br />\n<br />\n至於譚仔三哥，於最新4月13日的招聘日中，以最高17000元及17,500元招聘侍應和廚房／洗碗員，亦相當接近每月工資中位數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚仔算唔算香港本地飲食龍頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626fc7f31735625528a7e41ab8244932e3cc8d22","tid":2492482,"uid":85427,"like":259,"dislike":4,"score":255,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"首先對手要唔驚熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379ae6fd2d4d1b73d94abc435c4426f4ce4e7940","tid":2492482,"uid":102487,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"返幾多個鐘先"},{"pid":"4278e8ea701a0e03ca7b9f18f7dbcc7698f173aa","tid":2492482,"uid":395580,"like":116,"dislike":2,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"廚房應該幾好做，跟住配方整<br />\n容易過車仔面<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a43ce1b90a341e023900542257486b9540a6ef2","tid":2492482,"uid":11148,"like":184,"dislike":1,"score":183,"quote":{"pid":"626fc7f31735625528a7e41ab8244932e3cc8d22","tid":2492482,"uid":85427,"like":259,"dislike":4,"score":255,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"首先對手要唔驚熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"唔明,你講用手拎碗米線?我見依加係推車仔,好高級下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5536